      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "GO JO (2) is a capable type and proved too classy last time to win by 2 lengths at this track in a handy 22.50 beating Lord Shylock. Great chance to get the job done again. ONTARIO (8) has a strong record this journey with six wins and a minor from 12 starts. Below best last time at this track (22.46) in a Best 8, finishing a 10 length fifth. Can hit the frame with the right run. MAHOGANY DRIVE (1) draws the rails and gets chance to find form. Last time finished last over 383m at this track beaten 7 lengths (22.99) behind GO JO in a Grade 5 /MDN on March 8. A forward showing wouldn't surprise. SO NAIVE (4) is a last-start placegetter with solid claims again.",
